
#   LEO'S ROUTE 

#   DAY 0

label leo_D0_A:

    scene mcbedroom

    "The figurine box slowly levitates towards me and lands on my hands softly. Mystery Sponsor waits giddily at the thrill of my impending luck or misfortune."

    "I hold on to the corner of the film-laminated bag, my nerves crazy for whatever savior's inside."

    "Mystery Sponsor's default enthusiasm doesn't help my case in that manner. With a deep breath, I tear it open without looking."

    "I gradually peek through the tear and see a smidge of Leo's Hair Color. I shake it out of its container into my hand and see that it's..."

    "A cute, colorful figurine."

    "It dons baggy jeans, chunky shoes, a cropped oversized sleeveless hoodie, too many belts, and lots of thick rubber wristbands."

    "It's like a cohesive mess."

    "It's cute."

    "I fish out the figurine's card ticket that comes with it."

    "Leo, huh?"

    show sponsor_hyped

    sponsor "Let me see, let me see!"

    show sponsor_sweatingbeads

    sponsor "Oh. Eesh. Ooh boy."

    mc "Wh— What do you mean by that?"

    "MS jumps around back and forth, contemplating and muttering in its breath."

    show sponsor_thinking

    sponsor "Would it be...? No. But will it...? HMM."

    show sponsor_neutral

    sponsor "I'm sure it's nothing."

    show sponsor_thinking

    sponsor "Probably."

    "I look back at what's making him act like this. The colorful arrays it dons made its angry expression unnoticed."

    show sponsor_neutral

    sponsor "Well, nothing we can do now. Let me juuuust stamp your card aaaaand..."

    show sponsor_happy

    sponsor "You're good to go!"

    "I feel something shaking. It's too weak to be an earthquake, and it's definitely too strong for THAT kind of toy (I neither refuse nor agree to any claims), and see that it's coming from my hand."

    "The figurine was shaking on its own."

    "What I thought to remember, its plastered angry expression became angrier when I looked at it again, for what I hallucinate to be looking at Mystery Sponsor."

    mc "What's happening?!"

    show sponsor_sweatingbeads

    sponsor "Yeeeeah, you should probably definitely take cover."

    hide sponsor_sweatingbeads

    "The sudden impact made me fly off from where I was standing. I'm unharmed, but I definitely lost my footing."

    "I am on the floor on all fours, coughing. My room is completely covered in thick white clouds, making it hard to see anything."

    "What is going on?!"

    mc "{i}*cough*{/i} Mystery Sponsor? {i}*cough cough*{/i}"

    "I see a silhouette."

    "That must be Mystery Sponsor!"

    mc "{i}*cough cough*{/i} Hey! {i}*cough*{/i} Over here!"

    "I crawl towards bit by bit, navigating through the mountains of my hordes lying around."

    "The silhouette seems to be bigger than Mystery Sponsor, but he's probably shapeshifted into something. Some protection, maybe."

    "I hear Mystery Sponsor."

    sponsor "N-now, now. There's no need to escalate like this, Leo. You have to remember-"

    "Leo?"

    leo "{i}Ikaw...{/i}"

    "I close a bit to see Mystery Sponsor's tiny fish silhouette. This one is much, much taller, and stands with such exhaustion and... anger?"

    leo "{i}Ikaw... putangina ka...{/i}"

    sponsor "Buddy, pal, friend, uh... {i}Pare{/i}! Let's all take a chill pill, aaaaaaand whatdoyousaydoaodoverwithyourbuddypal?"

    leo "MS!!!"

    "His roar is deafening. Through the smoke, a chair pierces through, aiming towards me."

    "I duck."

    "My wooden, Greetings Feline tea chair is dismantled from the sheer force of his throw against the wall."

