label leo_D0_AA:

    # "WHAT THE FUCK" option

    mc "WHAT THE FUCK?!"

    "I'm so over this already."

    "This is DANGEROUS."

    "I can DIE."

    "And most importantly, those are MY stuff he's throwing!!!"

    mc "MYSTERY SPONSOR? WHERE ARE YOU!"

    show sponsor_neutral

    sponsor "Yellow. You called?"

    mc "What the fuck is happening?"

    "The silhouette is still thrashing around and throwing things in every direction."

    show sponsor_thinking

    sponsor "Hm! I think he is still thrashing around and throwing things in every direction."

    mc "Do you think this is a FUCKING JOKE-"

    show sponsor_happy

    mc "Not to worry!"

    show sponsor_thinking

    sponsor "I believe he is experiencing some sort of dissonance from being trapped for years in a small prison!"

    show sponsor_neutral

    sponsor "...Or he has a shark with him for a week."

    show sponsor_thinking
    
    sponsor "Shark week is the term, if I may recall?"

    show sponsor_happy

    sponsor "Your kind is so dangerous! Having apex predators as pets!"

    mc "Oh, interesting— I. DON'T. CARE. MAKE HIM STOP!"

    hide sponsor_happy

    jump leo_D0_B

label leo_D0_AB:

    "This is not going well. If only things were clean, maybe he wouldn't be able to throw things around, and I especially wouldn't be in this mess."

    "It's as if it's some sort of divine punishment from the gods."

    "Or a small fish in a suit."

    mc "Hey! Let's take a breather!"

    mc "It must be scary being here, but I'm here!"

    "I see the same silhouette who's winding up and throws through the thick fog. It feels like time is moving slowly. I see what he threw at us."

    "Is— Is that— you've got to be kidding me."

    "That's my 1:1 {i}1982 Super Cult Leader Lamb Chinaware Collectible{/i} from the hit retro game {i}Super Cult Leader: Lamberino!{/i}"

    "The ONLY one of its kind!"

    "I duck just in the nick of time, my 1:1 {i}1982 Super Cult Leader Lamb Chinaware{/i} from the hit retro game {i}Super Cult Leader: Lamberino.{/i}"

    "I see the shards on the ground, and for a moment, I feel like I saw the soul (money and dopamine) leaving its shattered, rare china body."

    mc "That's it!"

    show sponsor_wtf

    sponsor "What are you doing?"

    mc "What does it look like I'm doing?"

    mc "I'm TRYING to clean up YOUR mess."

    show sponsor_thinking

    sponsor "Hm! That's interesting."

    show sponsor_happy

    sponsor "You keep up the good work, then!"

    mc "...Thanks?"

    hide sponsor_happy

    "Seriously?????"

    jump leo_D0_B

label leo_D0_B:

    "We stopped when we couldn't hear the chaos. The air becomes heavy and there's a hard lump in my throat, trying not to make a noise."

    "Then, footsteps break the silence with the dragging of heavy furniture."

    show sponsor_wtf

    sponsor "Alright, that's my cue."

    show sponsor_neutral

    "Good luck!"

    mc "Wa-wait!! Mystery Sponsor wait-"

    hide sponsor_neutral

    "Before I could keep him from leaving, he vanished."

    "His footsteps are getting closer."

    "I try to escape, fearing I wouldn't see the incoming projectile of my early death should I break away my contact, but my back meets the wall."

    "Can he NOT see the size difference between the man he wants to kill and me?!"

    # FURNITURE is a placeholder until the Tech Script is updated

    "With a grunt and a swift motion, time feels so slow as I see the FURNITURE that's coming my way."

    "I couldn't do anything but close my eyes and brace for impact. It was a nice run, whatever life that was."

    "What I prepared myself for the pain didn't come at all."

    "Instead, I see Mystery Sponsor, who tries to rub off sweat with its limbless fish body from its nonexistent forehead."

    "The clouds are gone, my living room's even messier with my broken collectibles lying around, and the perpetrator of it all..."

